---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="IBC for Business Owners | IBC Academy" description="How business owners use Infinite Banking to fund growth without banks, maintain liquidity, and build tax-efficient wealth while running their companies.">

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO — Business Owner Landing Page
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 lg:py-24">
    <!-- Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FAF9F6] via-navy-light/10 to-[#FAF9F6]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top_right,_rgba(201,168,76,0.08)_0%,_transparent_60%)]"></div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in-up text-center">
        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#B8860B]/10 border border-[#B8860B]/20 mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8860B]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-[#B8860B] text-sm font-semibold">For Business Owners</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Headline -->
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-[#1A1A1A] leading-tight tracking-tight">
          Fund Your Business Growth<br class="hidden md:block" />
          <span class="text-[#B8860B]">Without Asking a Bank</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-[#4A4A4A] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          What if you could access capital for equipment, inventory, or expansion on your terms — no credit checks, no collateral, no waiting for approval?
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Buttons -->
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/webinar" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold to-gold-dark text-navy-900 font-extrabold text-lg rounded-xl hover:from-gold-light hover:to-gold transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-gold/30 hover:shadow-gold/50">
            Watch the Free Webinar
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/discovery" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-slate-300 text-[#1A1A1A] font-bold rounded-xl hover:border-[#B8860B]/50 hover:text-[#B8860B] transition-all">
            Talk to Brad
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE BUSINESS OWNER'S DILEMMA
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white/50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in-up text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">
          Sound <span class="text-[#B8860B]">Familiar?</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">"The bank wants my firstborn for a loan"</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-[#4A4A4A]">Collateral requirements, personal guarantees, endless paperwork — and they still might say no.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">"Great opportunity, no capital"</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-[#4A4A4A]">You see the deal. You know the ROI. But your cash is tied up and the bank moves too slow.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">"Taxes are eating my profits"</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-[#4A4A4A]">You're making money, but between income tax, capital gains, and estate tax, the government takes more than you keep.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">"I'm building the business, not my wealth"</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-[#4A4A4A]">All your money goes back into the business. Great for growth, but where's your personal financial security?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       THE IBC SOLUTION FOR BUSINESS OWNERS
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in-up text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">
          How Business Owners Use <span class="text-[#B8860B]">IBC</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[#4A4A4A] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The Infinite Banking Concept gives you a private pool of capital you control — accessible anytime, for any purpose, with no approval needed.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#B8860B]/15 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-[#B8860B] font-bold text-xl">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">Fund Equipment & Inventory</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[#4A4A4A]">Need a new truck? More inventory for the busy season? Take a policy loan, make the purchase, then pay yourself back on your own schedule. No bank approval, no interest rate negotiations, no waiting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#B8860B]/15 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-[#B8860B] font-bold text-xl">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">Bridge Cashflow Gaps</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[#4A4A4A]">Receivables are 60 days out but payroll is Friday? Access your policy cash value immediately. Make payroll, then replenish when the client pays. Your policy keeps growing either way.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#B8860B]/15 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-[#B8860B] font-bold text-xl">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">Seize Opportunities Fast</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[#4A4A4A]">Competitor going out of business? Real estate deal with a 48-hour window? By the time a bank approves your loan, the opportunity is gone. Policy loans fund within days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#B8860B]/15 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <span class="text-[#B8860B] font-bold text-xl">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">Build Tax-Advantaged Wealth</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[#4A4A4A]">Policy cash value grows tax-deferred. Death benefit passes tax-free. Policy loans aren't taxable events. You're building wealth for your family while funding your business.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       KEY INSIGHT
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-900 to-navy-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        The Key Insight
      </h2>
      <blockquote class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-slate-300 italic leading-relaxed">
        "When you finance through a bank, the interest you pay builds <em>their</em> wealth. When you finance through your policy, the interest you pay builds <em>your</em> wealth."
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-6 text-[#C9A84C] font-semibold">
        — The Banking Function, from Nelson Nash's "Becoming Your Own Banker"
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       WHAT YOU GET
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="fade-in-up text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A1A1A]">
          A Properly Designed IBC Policy <span class="text-[#B8860B]">Gives You</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-2">Guaranteed Liquidity</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#4A4A4A]">Access your cash value anytime, for any reason, no questions asked.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-2">Uninterrupted Compound Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#4A4A4A]">Your full cash value keeps earning dividends even while you borrow against it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-2">Tax Advantages</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#4A4A4A]">Tax-deferred growth, tax-free death benefit, policy loans aren't taxable.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-2">Flexible Repayment</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#4A4A4A]">Pay back on your schedule. No mandatory payments. You set the terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-2">Asset Protection</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#4A4A4A]">In many states, life insurance cash value is protected from creditors and lawsuits.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1A1A1A] mb-2">Legacy Planning</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#4A4A4A]">Death benefit provides for your family and can fund buy-sell agreements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
       CTA — NEXT STEPS
       ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1A1A1A] via-[#2A2A2A] to-[#1A1A1A]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">
        Ready to <span class="text-[#C9A84C]">Become Your Own Banker?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-10">
        Join the free 45-minute webinar to see exactly how IBC works — with real numbers, real examples, and zero sales pressure.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/webinar" class="inline-flex items-center px-10 py-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold to-gold-dark text-navy-900 font-extrabold text-xl rounded-xl hover:from-gold-light hover:to-gold transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-gold/30 hover:shadow-gold/50">
          Watch the Free Webinar
          <svg class="ml-3 w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/free-guide" class="inline-flex items-center px-10 py-5 border-2 border-white/30 text-white font-bold text-xl rounded-xl hover:border-[#C9A84C] hover:text-[#C9A84C] transition-all">
          Get the Free Guide
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">
        Education first, always. No pressure, no obligation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
